import org.apache.spark.ml.Pipeline
import org.apache.spark.ml.classification.DecisionTreeClassifier
import org.apache.spark.ml.classification.DecisionTreeClassificationModel
import org.apache.spark.ml.feature.{VectorAssembler,StringIndexer,OneHotEncoder, IndexToString, VectorIndexer}
import org.apache.spark.ml.evaluation.MulticlassClassificationEvaluator
import org.apache.spark.sql._
// Load the data stored in LIBSVM format as a DataFrame.
// val data = sqlContext.read.format("libsvm").load("data/mllib/sample_libsvm_data.txt")
// ymblackactdf.drop("registip","registcity")
def loaddata(cust:String="cust2016q1data",ymdata:String="ymdata"):DataFrame={
var ymblackactdf=sqlContext.sql(s"""
select case when ym.id is not null then cast(1 as double) else 0 end as label,
cust.id,cust.age,cust.sex,cust.status,cust.registdevice,cust.ctime,
-- case when length(cust.registip)>0 then cust.registip else "no data" end as registip,
-- case when length(cust.registcity)>0 then cust.registcity else "no data" end as registcity,
case when length(cust.registfrom)>0 then cust.registfrom else "no data" end as registfrom,
-- idcardtime,phonetime,emailtime,registtime,wxopenidtime,jxtime,timestamp,
case when cust.deviceid is not null then cast(1 as double) else 0 end as hasdeviceid,
case when cust.idcardtime is not null then cast(1 as double) else 0 end as isvalidatename,
case when cust.phonetime is not null then cast(1 as double) else 0 end as isvalidatemobi,
case when cust.emailtime is not null then cast(1 as double) else 0  end as isvalidateemil,
case when cust.wxopenidtime is not null then cast(1 as double) else 0 end as haswxopenid,
case when cust.jxtime is not null then cast(1 as double) else 0 end as hasjxaccount,

case when cust.qq is not null then cast(1 as double) else 0 end as hasqq, 
case when cust.weixin is not null then cast(1 as double) else 0 end as hasweixin,
case when cust.weibo is not null then cast(1 as double) else 0 end as hasweibo,
case when cust.address is not null then cast(1 as double) else 0 end as hasaddress,
case when cust.inviterid is not null then cast(1 as double) else 0 end as isinvite,
case when cust.customerserviceid is not null then cast(1 as double) else 0 end as hascustservice,

draw.* ,rech.*
,inve.*,asse.*,fund.*,acti.*
from $cust cust
left join $ymdata ym on (cust.id=ym.id)-- ymblackdata 

left join(
select customerId,type drawtype,count(customerId) drawnum,sum(amount) sumdrawamount,avg(amount) avgdrawamount,max(amount) maxdrawamount,min(amount) mindrawamount,var_pop(amount) stddevdrawamount,stddev(timestamp) stddevdrawtime 
from ymdrawdata 
where status=2
group by customerId,type --0-普通取现 1-即时取现  2存管提现
--order by timestamp desc
) draw on cust.id=draw.customerId

left join(
select customerId rechcustomerId,type rechtype,count(customerId) rechnum,sum(amount) sumrechamount,avg(amount) avgrechamount,max(amount) maxrechamount,min(amount) minrechamount,var_pop(amount) stddevrechamount,stddev(timestamp) stddevrechtime 
from ymrechargedata 
where status=2
group by customerId,type --1:连连支付充值,0:汇付天下
--order by timestamp desc
) rech on cust.id=rechcustomerId

left join(
select uid inveuid,count(uid) invenum ,mode--0-普通 1-life
-- ,period--实际项目时间
,typeStatus--0未启用  1启用
,periodType--期限　如 ：90天，180天
,sum(investAmount) suminveamount,avg(investAmount) avginveamount,max(investAmount) maxinveamount,min(investAmount) mininveamount,var_pop(investAmount) stddevinveamount--投资金额
,investType-- 0-直投转让 1-非直投转让
,yield,isJx,device invedevice,stddev(investTimestamp) stddevinvetime 
from yminvedata 
where investstatus=1--0-待支付 1-已支付 2-已失效 
and isx=0 --定期
-- and typeStatus=1
group by uid,mode,periodType,investType,device,yield,isjx,typeStatus
--order by investTimestamp desc
) inve on cust.id=inveuid

left join (
select uid asseuid,count(uid) assenum,type assetype--1转入2转出
,sum(amount) sumasseamount,avg(amount) avgasseamount,max(amount) maxasseamount,min(amount) minasseamount,var_pop(amount) stddevasseamount
,sum(accountInterest) sumaccountInterest,avg(accountInterest) avgaccountInterest,max(accountInterest) maxaccountInterest,min(accountInterest) minaccountInterest,var_pop(accountInterest) stddevaccountInterest --账户利息
,sum(accountAmount) sumaccountAmount,avg(accountAmount) avgaccountAmount,max(accountAmount) maxaccountAmount,min(accountAmount) minaccountAmount,var_pop(accountAmount) stddevaccountAmount--账户本金
-- ,accountInAmount --账户待转入额
-- ,accountOutAmount
,sum(accountTotalInterest) sumaccountTotalInterest,avg(accountTotalInterest) avgaccountTotalInterest,max(accountTotalInterest) maxaccountTotalInterest,min(accountTotalInterest) minaccountTotalInterest,var_pop(accountTotalInterest) stddevaccountTotalInterest --账户累计收益
,device assedevice,stddev(timestamp) stddevassetime  
from ymassedata 
where status=1
group by uid,device,type
--order by timestamp desc
) asse on cust.id=asseuid

left join (
select uid funduid,count(uid) fundnum,type fundtype
,sum(amount) sumfundamount,avg(amount) avgfundamount,max(amount) maxfundamount,min(amount) minfundamount,var_pop(amount) stddevfundamount,stddev(timestamp) stddevfundtime
,sum(total) sumtotal,avg(total) avgtotal,max(total) maxtotal,min(total) mintotal,var_pop(total) stddevtotal--总额=冻结+可用+代收
-- ,frozen -- 冻结
-- ,avaliable -- 可用
-- ,collectedCapital --待收本金
-- ,collectedInterest --待收利息
,sum(totalInvestment)  sumtotalInvestment,avg(totalInvestment) avgtotalInvestment,max(totalInvestment) maxtotalInvestment,min(totalInvestment) mintotalInvestment,var_pop(totalInvestment) stddevtotalInvestment-- 累计投资额
,sum(totalInterest) sumtotalInterest,avg(totalInterest) avgtotalInterest,max(totalInterest) maxtotalInterest,min(totalInterest) mintotalInterest,var_pop(totalInterest) stddevtotalInterest --累计收益额
,sum(totalCash) sumtotalCash,avg(totalCash) avgtotalCash,max(totalCash) maxtotalCash,min(totalCash) mintotalCash,var_pop(totalCash) stddevtotalCash --累计提现额
,sum(totalRecharge) sumtotalRecharge,avg(totalRecharge) avgtotalRecharge,max(totalRecharge) maxtotalRecharge,min(totalRecharge) mintotalRecharge,var_pop(totalRecharge) stddevtotalRecharge --累计充值额
,sum(totalActivity) sumtotalActivity,avg(totalActivity) avgtotalActivity,max(totalActivity) maxtotalActivity,min(totalActivity) mintotalActivity,var_pop(totalActivity) stddevtotalActivity --活动累计收益
from ymfunddata 
where type=41 --投资 43 回款
group by uid,type
) fund on cust.id=funduid

left join (
select uid actiuid,count(id) actinum,count(nid) nnum,awardType--0-红包 1-利率 2-优先权 3-实物 4-随机红包
,stddev(useTime) stddevtime--使用时间
,sum(valuation) sumvaluation,avg(valuation) avgvaluation,max(valuation) maxvaluation,min(valuation) minvaluation,var_pop(valuation) stddevvaluation
-- ,activityAwardType--0-红包 1-利率 2-优先权 3-实物
,type actitype--0-主动领取 1-系统循环发放 2-系统一次性发放
-- ,activityStatus--1 启用  0 锁定
-- ,sendMsg--0-不发送 1-发送
-- ,number--一次性发放数量
-- ,gainType--0-领取条件 1-使用条件
-- ,useType--0-领取条件 1-使用条件
from ymactidata 
where status=1--0-未使用 1-已使用 2-已过期
group by uid,awardType,type--,sendMsg,number,gainType,useType
--order by timestamp desc
) acti on cust.id=actiuid
--where FLOOR(cust.ctime/1000000000)>20160101 and FLOOR(cust.ctime/1000000000)<20160115 or FLOOR(cust.ctime/1000000000)>20160301 and FLOOR(cust.ctime/1000000000)<20160315
""")
val ymblackactdf1=ymblackactdf.na.fill(value="no data",cols=Array("registfrom"))
val ymblackactdf2=ymblackactdf1.na.fill(0)
// ymblackactdf2.limit(3).show
ymblackactdf2
}
